&lt;p&gt;In the useCreateAppRouter.tsx, at L66, &lt;a href="https://github.com/twentyhq/twenty/blob/main/packages/twenty-front/src/modules/app/components/SettingsRoutes.tsx#L409" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;SettingsRoute&lt;/a&gt; is defined as below:&lt;br&gt;
